Springtrap Character Information Species Animatronic Rabbit Color Olive green/yellow First Appears Night 2 onwards

Springtrap is the main and only physical antagonist in Five Nights at Freddy's 3. He is a massively-damaged rabbit animatronic/springlock suit, as well as the only antagonist that can kill the player and give them a Game Over, as the phantom animatronics can only jumpscare the player and impair their vision and/or hearing
